name: Wookiee (V)
Lore: 'Wookiees are known to be fierce warriors. Combine high technology with a primitive lifestyle. Escaped Imperial slavery after the Battle of Endor.',
Text: 'May move as a ''react''. While with another Wookiee, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. If about to be lost, may place any cards on him in owner''s Used Pile and may draw top card from Reserve Deck.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
